<title>USA: Lancit names Susan Solomon chairman/CEO.</title>
<headline>Lancit names Susan Solomon chairman/CEO.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Lancit Media Entertainment said Tuesday that Susan Solomon had been named chairman and chief executive officer, effective immediately.</p>
<p>Solomon joins Lancit from Sony Corp, where she served as president and chief executive officer of Sony Worldwide Networks.</p>
<p>Solomon succeeds Cecily Truett, who was named Lancit co-president. Truett will share the presidency with Larry Lancit.</p>
<p>Lancit is a creator and producer of children's television programs.</p>
